**Converged Plan**

- Retitle the proposal to **“Morpho Collateral Risk Transparency Layer.”**
- Position it as a **public transparency infrastructure grant** with an **experimental modeling track**, not as a production-ready full-stack risk model.

**Document Architecture**

- Split the submission into **three documents**.
- **Main RFC:** problem, proof of work, scoped deliverables, team, budget, sustainability.
- **Technical appendix:** six-factor model, GARCH/HMM, Merton/PD design, math reference.
- **Evidence appendix:** live outputs, claim register, screenshots, retroactive incident case studies.

